column1: text
Look what I gotttt
Life was in its prime 2013-2019 Ngl
A girl got fucked on stream and only got a 7 day ban. What the fuck bro. Free Speed & JIDION this shit is not right
Andrew hit me and told me to tell everyone his last message to the world. So… Andrew Tate’s last message to the internet - here it is.
I got swatted last night, very very scary. I’m okay. I love you guys. Also speed got swatted aswell, we just got off the phone he’s okay! Sick world we live in man.
Just found out this
Adin Ross X Andrew Tate discord stream locked in for next week. I’m gonna do a reverse e date and put 8 girls on a date with Andrew.
THE NEXT CHAPTER
It’s time.
F*ck everyone
It’s official call of duty black ops 2 is the greatest video game to ever exist. Most fun, addicting game ever. No debate, idc what anybody says.
Literal innocent lives are being lost as I write this tweet. This is heartbreaking .. praying for Ukraine
gg :)
AR X AB
Merry Christmas
This lakers team is the worst thing I’ve ever seen. LeBron does everything and he’s 39 years old. Russell Westbrook is so horrible it’s so sad. Millions of dollars to throw turnovers
Couple days before Christmas. Like this tweet and reply with what you need and I’ll bless y’all and shoot some of u guys a dm :)

I’m obviously trolling with the sue shit.  If you watch my streams you’d know that, this ain’t beef so stop dragging it.  I am not on any gang shit I do not have 40s. Gunnas. Any sort of type of weapon machinery. I am a young handsome streamer who sits at home all day

Ah hell nah. Just woke up and youngboy fr dissed me … talking about gunnas laying with me , which is a gun. Well, I guess it’s time to sue  Say to that streamer or YouTube or whatever he is stop playing with me bitch Cause man like that know the gunnas laying with me bitch”
Stephen curry is the greatest shooter of all time. It’s that simple
Thank you Kanye and Drake for literally coming together and having the best concert of all time. Free Larry
